product.name: Otani Purifying Treatment
product.description: The Purifying facial is focused on clearing active breakouts and congestion as well as destroying acne causing bacteria. The unique multi step process uses different modalities such as LED treatment and High frequency as well as advanced cosmeceuticals to get results fast. (Congested, Problematic skin types)

product.name: Otani Teen Facial
product.description: Focused on Deep cleaning and clearing of congestion and acne causing bacteria. Soothing mask and massage is also included in this treatment. Your Teen will leave with comprehensive knowledge of their skin and how to look after it simply and easily at home.

product.name: OxyGeneo 3in1 Facial
product.description: The OxyGeneo treatment is an innovative facial that delivers 3 skin renewing anti-aging treatments simultaneously: exfoliation, infusion and oxygenation. This exclusive combination improves skin tone, evens texture and nourishes the complexion giving a balanced healthy glow. Includes blissful aromatherapy massage and customised mask, serum and moisturiser application. (All skin types).

product.name: Express Microdermabrasion
product.description: A very effective anti-aging resurfacing treatment that smoothes coarse textured skin and softens fine lines and wrinkles. The gentle resurfacing also helps with scarring gentle resurfacing scarring and superficial hyper-pigmentation (age spots).

product.name: Otani UltraDiamond
product.description: The most indulgent Microdermabrasion treatment you will ever experience. With all the benefits of microdermabrasion such as smoothing coarse textured skin and softening fine lines and wrinkles, scarring and hyper-pigmentation. This facial is set apart with the luxurious aromatherapy massage and Icy globes massage to soothe and calm the skin as well as minimise pore size. LED is used to regulate natural oil production whilst stimulating collagen and elastin and minimising redness and wrinkles. Finished with Rose Quartz GuaSha massage it cant be beat. (All skin types).

product.name: Dermaplaning Facial
product.description: Dermaplaning is a form of exfoliation where an aesthetician grade, sterile blade is stroked along the skin at an angle to gently “shave off” dead skin cells and peach fuzz from the epidermis. Pineapple and Papaya enzyme Gel is then massaged into the skin to smooth out any remaining unevenness and brighten skin. Collagen and Hyaluronic sheet mask is then applied to deeply hydrate and plump skin cells. Finished with LED treatment regulating natural oil production, stimulating collagen and elastin and minimising redness and wrinkles. Dermaplaning allows for better penetration of treatment products. Suitable in the treatment of, Fine lines and wrinkles, uneven skin tone, couperose (tiny vessels near the surface of the skin) and congested pores.

product.name: Thermal Detox Facial
product.description: The new Thermal Detox Facial from Nimue is a 4-in-1 treatment that deeply cleanses the skin surface and pores, Detoxifies, Oxygenates and Exfoliates with pumpkin enzymes and AHA’s to dissolve the 'glue' between skin cells, allowing them to slough off. This treatment refines pore size, softens fine lines, softens skin texture and improves overall radiance. Many say they've never experienced a treatment like it before, its thermal charcoal properties deliver a soothing warming sensation.

product.name: Collagen Induction Therapy (Dermapen)
product.description: (min. cost shown, max. cost 150) The Dermapen treatments use a precise needling technique that results in increased collagen and elastin. You can expect smoother skin that looks refreshed, restored and youthful. Skin needling promotes scarless healing and natural collagen reproduction, similar to fractional laser treatments and laser resurfacing, but without the side effects and down time. Collagen Induction Therapy is one of the most advanced skin rejuvenation therapies available today for the treatment of: Fine lines and wrinkles, Scars (acne, surgical and burns), Large Pores, and Overall skin Rejuvenation.

product.name: Dermaenergy Berry Peel
product.description: The Dermaenergy Berry Peel is a unique blend of 6 different berries - Blueberry, Raspberry, Strawberry, Maqui Berry, Cranberry, Bearberry. This indulgent and luxurious Peel delivers instantly softer skin. Rejuvenating, Energising and Brightening. (Suitable for All skin types and Pigmented skin).

product.name: Dermaenergy Enzyme Peel
product.description: Fruit enzymes of Mango, Pineapple, Papaya, Pomegranate, Starfruit, Passionfruit and Kiwi. This indulgent and luxurious Peel delivers instantly softer skin. Rejuvenating, Energising and Brightening. (Suitable for All skin types and Pigmented skin).

product.name: Pumpkin Peel
product.description: Pumpkin Peel is an effective exfoliator derived from pumpkin. Pumpkin proteolytic enzymes help to digest proteins that have accumulated on the skin's surface. Enhance cellular renewal through exfoliation for a smooth, even skin texture. Skin will instantly feel softer, refined and energised. Acne will be cleared quickly. Skin refined and instantly dewy. (All skin types, acne / pigment).

product.name: Fusion Peel
product.description: A multi-acid and multi-enzyme peeling solution suitable for all skin types and issues. Minimal irritation, almost no downtime, and fabulous corrective action. An amazing Fusion of exfoliating agents that produce a number of skin benefits, such as clearing acne, reducing age spots, melasma, and improving skin texture and fine lines and wrinkles.
